column5: Awww so cute      All kidding aside, that's a huuuge fish!
I'm thinkin' the Mr. Mercer is gonna have something to say about this...
Did y'all ever see the pic of the Catfish Ray Charles caught?  .. no?  ... neither did he!
Hey is that real?? Cause that just blew my mind!!!
Yes it is a wels and they get even bigger than that.
Ya beat me to it. Wels catfish get massive. I believe, but could be wrong, that they are the largest freshwater fish.............
